{"tid":2320427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"棉花棒係好唔環保，當三日用一次，每隻耳仔用1枝[減少使用棉花棒: 方案探討]","createTime":"2020-12-10T21:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T03:18:03.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6d70e1486930f148edfb7208915282246a7439","tid":2320427,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:39:50.000Z","msg":"一年每個人會產生 243.3 枝嘅棉花棒，而呢堆棉花棒中蕊個膠軸係極難自然分解，動物誤食嘅後過可想而知。700萬人就用咗過10億枝棉花棒<br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做，其實大家會發現棉花棒係有分膠軸同紙軸，膠軸就係唔環保嗰種，紙軸就環保啲<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係環保，都唔一定用棉花棒，用去耳垢劑比棉花棒安全得多，又唔驚整親隻耳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929fce48457eb84a5adb12e9d00a6b01ff459f56","tid":2320427,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:40:26.000Z","msg":"開錯台，請無視"},{"pid":"b15b62762ff62c4aaac87eafbbca7586ad086025","tid":2320427,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"仲有銀個隻 耳搲"},{"pid":"ac0880590aec9f87a8dc90fa40bda4e7dec664a3","tid":2320427,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"從來唔挖耳屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}